{"tid":161131,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"兩國互抵制！首爾計程車標示「拒載中國人」　飛陸航班大減","createTime":"2017-03-18T10:18:32.000Z","updateTime":"2017-03-18T18:21:48.000Z","uid":62257,"like":53,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":0,"replies":[{"pid":"2bc8b32f2de7f2f078e6c96b8c3fc6a4abc6f22d","tid":161131,"uid":62257,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-03-18T10:18:32.000Z","msg":"<a href=\"http://www.setn.com/News.aspx?NewsID=233729\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=http%3A%2F%2Fwww.setn.com%2FNews.aspx%3FNewsID%3D233729&d=9ZkxwAQN0Q6nkyzE8ymhdC7bS0i5kAixZS1hjGmvpwM%3D&h=dc9f395a\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=http%3A%2F%2Fwww.setn.com%2FNews.aspx%3FNewsID%3D233729&h=40e08d48\" target=\"_blank\">http://www.setn.com/News.aspx?NewsID=233729</a><br />\n中國大陸與南韓的「薩德」風暴繼續延燒，現在連中韓直飛航線都被迫大砍159個班次，大陸可能在15日舉行的的消費者大會上修理南韓企業，一波接一波的攻勢，現在把南韓民眾惹毛了！首爾有計程車就掛上「拒載中國人」的標示，還有網友大肆慶功說「沒有中國人的首爾，變得超棒」。 <br />\n<br />\n商場門口冷冷清清，內部也是小貓兩三隻，受到中韓薩德爭議影響，不光中國境內的南韓商場沒生意。<br />\n<br />\n浦項市市長：「我們可能會再用別的管道來吸引中國遊客。」<br />\n<br />\n就連直飛航線都大量縮減，大韓航空和韓亞航空，大砍169個班次。航空業者：「因為機票預定量不足，所以我們只好暫時減班，航線以後可能會改成東南亞或日本。」<br />\n<br />\n南韓企業還擔心，大陸會在3月15日的消費者晚會上拿南韓公司當標靶，但大陸的抵制不只傷到南韓遊客必去的觀光勝地濟州島，一向僱用許多大陸人，但現在「祖國」遊客不來，這些打工族開始擔心要丟工作。大陸留學生：「留學生在這邊比較困難吧，留學生在這邊，待遇沒有以前這麼好了。」<br />\n<br />\n雖然中國官方民間大力推行禁韓令，但南韓民眾私底下卻覺得，少了陸客的首爾，清爽多了。<br />\n<br />\n新聞主播：「這是首爾的計程車，計程車的保險桿上貼著拒載中國客。」不光是中國大陸反南韓，南韓民間也反中國大陸，可見他們寧可經濟受影響也不想看到陸客。（整理：實習編輯施鈺潔）"},{"pid":"3ba8d48b8ef34bac53b36974980c47e28e118fe9","tid":161131,"uid":60831,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-03-18T10:20:12.000Z","msg":"南韓好波 <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"88df860533e217b9e63e73f8f3cf207eec0130b0","tid":161131,"uid":27451,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-03-18T10:23:30.000Z","msg":"圖啦？唔好學強國撚打飛機呀"},{"pid":"457e42ccebf22473e26d6fa3b9633b3e0a66a079","tid":161131,"uid":39800,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-03-18T10:30:35.000Z","msg":"好！"},{"pid":"f54980077d935794174514d038d312a0d7399a5b","tid":161131,"uid":35882,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-03-18T10:32:10.000Z","msg":"狗咬狗<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/hoho.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/hoho.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"e158f6de78312211afed62878e064bbe9c21c808","tid":161131,"uid":37735,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-03-18T10:34:16.000Z","msg":"當年捐金<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/good.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n依家抵制支那<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/good.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"935b7855a958bc367dc8becafb390d21fc7f9ae0","tid":161131,"uid":37735,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-03-18T10:35:06.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>當年捐金<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/good.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n依家抵制支那<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/good.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n<br />\n泡茶是<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n但係支那前 緊係支持<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"602943c906bf8f9923f2dc7ea0ba894a67e5a944","tid":161131,"uid":89608,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-03-18T10:39:08.000Z","msg":"中國真係好撚ON9, 咁樣同韓國互鬥, 又係益左美國助收漁人之利,<br />\n<br />\n而且鬥落去都係冇成果架啦, 成大個美國做後盾, 唔通搞搞下韓國會話, <br />\n<br />\n我錯啦, 我道歉改過啦咁咩,<br />\n<br />\n做一大堆選人不利己既野, 係鬥就直搗核心, 鬥美國, 夠唔夠膽先"},{"pid":"2e5d81a1f9b5fc0e8aa62dfb2d5686357a222130","tid":161131,"uid":20522,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-03-18T10:40:21.000Z","msg":"冇支那人先至係賣點<img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/36.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"17821821eb919dbf728c8f25536becfbb7b0da0d","tid":161131,"uid":45857,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-03-18T10:44:05.000Z","msg":"8月尾去日本, 好撚不安<img src=\"/assets/faces/fs/angel.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"1ade3b89955235ec3b15a81a9c8f05203b8ede99","tid":161131,"uid":7699,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-03-18T10:46:03.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>8月尾去日本, 好撚不安<img src=\"/assets/faces/fs/angel.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n可能過多幾個月到日本起薩德呢<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/biggrin.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"95bf6f5a900337c6af8106f0e1d3bf96b00e163b","tid":161131,"uid":55219,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-03-18T10:47:23.000Z","msg":"香港人幾時先可以有咁嘅骨氣唔做大陸人生意<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"9033392f74b80f8f4ed221d187fd63f02a080a7b","tid":161131,"uid":79563,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-03-18T10:49:10.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>當年捐金<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/good.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n依家抵制支那<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/good.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n<br />\n咪係, 南泡個國民民族性好團結<br />\n為國家捐金都得, 你支那人會唔會損金比支那國?<br />\n<br />\n(南泡有時柒還柒, 但真係好團結,有骨氣, 呢點港豬要學)"},{"pid":"50674f0c18d34263787c7863fbd00f82036226f0","tid":161131,"uid":11753,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-03-18T10:50:21.000Z","msg":"打鐵趁熱斷交喇喂<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"507c44a1a3b32d234a53ecba5eff4ff6a83e06d3","tid":161131,"uid":79563,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-03-18T10:55:34.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><blockquote>8月尾去日本, 好撚不安<img src=\"/assets/faces/fs/angel.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n可能過多幾個月到日本起薩德呢<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/biggrin.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n<br />\n沖繩部署F-22, 支那又唔抵制<br />\n<br />\n真係好神奇既智力"},{"pid":"4b5b1768533ffb1a9545c9b265ba2637c49ad3cb","tid":161131,"uid":51701,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-03-18T10:57:23.000Z","msg":"泡狗賤還賤<br />\n有骨氣"},{"pid":"c4a5ddcf396d403dd3956001b57cc2092204ca30","tid":161131,"uid":28031,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-03-18T10:57:58.000Z","msg":"中国邏輯"},{"pid":"e2c367c594